snippet.title: Robert Downey Jr Helps Revive Johnny Depp's Career : Sherlock Holmes 3
snippet.description:
Is Johnny Depp is Starring with Robert Downey jr in Sherlock Holmes 3? 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

Johnny Depp after being removed for ‘Pirates of Caribbean’ is now being thrown a huge lifeline to help save his career. Old friend and fellow former heIl-raiser Robert Downey Jr wants Johnny to co-star in his latest upcoming Sherlock Holmes film, due out next year.
